20uncontested%20from%20his%20father's%20constituency%20Mukto%2C%20that%20he%20truly%20began%20to%20carve%20out%20his%20political%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPema%20Khandu's%20rise%20was%20swift.%20Serving%20initially%20as%20the%20tourism%20minister%20in%20Nabam%20Tuki's%20Congress%20government%2C%20his%20leadership%20trajectory%20soared%20following%20a%20constitutional%20crisis%20in%20January%202016%20that%20led%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20president's%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20central%20rule%20was%20lifted%2C%20he%20became%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Kalikho%20Pul-led%20government%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20this%20government%20was%20short-lived.%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention%20restored%20Nabam%20Tuki%2C%20who%20soon%20resigned%2C%20and%20at%20just%2037%2C%20Pema%20Khandu%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20July%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Pema%20Khandu%20and%20his%20government%20have%20twice%20changed%20their%20party%20affiliation%20in%20quick%20succession%20-%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20People's%20Party%20of%20Arunachal%20(PPA)%20in%20September%202016%20and%20then%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20December%20of%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20three%20months%20into%20his%20term%2C%2043%20ruling%20Congress%20MLAs%20defected%20to%20the%20PPA%2C%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20internal%20discord%20led%20to%20his%20suspension%20from%20the%20PPA%2C%20Pema%20Khandu%20demonstrated%20resilience%20and%20adaptability%20by%20joining%20the%20BJP%20along%20with%20most%20PPA%20MLAs%2C%20securing%20his%20position%20and%20proving%20his%20majority%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Pema%20Khandu%20won%20from%20Mukto%20assembly%20seat%20for%20the%20second%20time%20and%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20without%20any%20political%20hindrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20Pema%20Khandu%20