ng%20to%20keep%20staff%20quiet%20about%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%20at%20Boeing's%20largest%20factory%20in%20Everett%2C%20Washington%2C%20%26quot%3Bwill%20hound%20mechanics%26quot%3B%20to%20keep%20quiet%20about%20safety%20and%20quality%20assurance%20concerns%2C%20a%20mechanic%20who%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20company%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjun%2F01%2Fboeing-safety-crisis-response-union-busting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boeing.com%2Fcompany%2Fabout-bca%2Feverett-production-facility%23anchor1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing's%20Everett%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20manufacturing%20buildings%2C%20produces%20the%20747%2C%20767%2C%20777%2C%20and%20787%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20factory%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20fixing%20the%20787%20Dreamliner%2C%20and%20the%20unnamed%20mechanic%20told%20the%20Guardian%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%26quot%3B%20faulty%20787%20jets%20waiting%20to%20be%20mended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20planes%20arriving%20at%20Everett%20come%20from%20Boeing's%20787%20Dreamliner%20Final%20Assembly%20building%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20which%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboeing.mediaroom.com%2F2011-06-10-Boeing-Opens-New-South-Carolina-787-Final-Assembly-Building%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopened%20in%202011%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mechanic%20added%20that%20people%20at%20the%20Everett%20site%20were%20%26quot%3Bin%20panic%20mode%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20that%20Boeing%20managers%20%26quot%3Bfinally%20figured%20out%20that%20they%20got%20more%20people%20that%20have%20no%20idea%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20than%20people%20that%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Guardian%20reported%20that%20Boeing%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20comment%20on%20claims%20that%20staff%20have%20been%20pressured%20not%20to%20raise%20concerns%20about%20quality%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20that%20work%20on%20the%20787s%20at%20the%20Everett%20factory%20was%20part%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bestablished%20verification%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20contacted%20Boeing%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aerospace%20manufacturer%20has%20faced%20increased%20scrutiny%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-crashes-groundings-timeline-737-max-777-air-force-tanker-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estring%20of%20safety%20issues%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20Alaska%20Airlines%20blowout%20in%20January%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fupdates-boeing-737-9-max-aircraft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrounding%20of%20171%20Max%209%20planes%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Authority%20(FAA)%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20claims%20made%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-workers-falsely-reported-performing-checks-on-787-wings-fuselage-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20quality%20engineer%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsgac.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FSalehpour-Testimony-24.04.17.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20observed%20the%20company%20start%20taking%20%26quot%3Bshortcuts%26quot%3B%20while%20working%20on%20the%20787%20in%20late%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatest-boeing-whistleblower-urges-planemaker-to-ground-all-787s-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Salehpour%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20believed%20the%20company%20had%20failed%20to%20adequately%20shim%20%E2%80%94%20or%20fill%20tiny%20gaps%20with%20a%20thin%20piece%20of%20material%20%E2%80%94%20parts%20affecting%20more%20than%201%2C000%20787s%20in%20service%2C%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Blikely%20to%20cause%20premature%20fatigue%20failure%20over%20time%20in%20two%20major%20airplane%20joints.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20shortcuts%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20%26quot%3Breduce%20bottlenecks%20in%20production%20and%20speed%20up%20production%20and%20delivery%20of%20787s.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20pushed%20back%20at%20the%20claims%20on%20its%20website%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20has%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20787%20Dreamliner%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20work%20done%20to%20ensure%20the%20quality%20and%20long-term%20safety%20of%20the%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaims%20about%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20the%20787%20are%20inaccurate%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20FAA%20ordered%20another%20investigation%20into%20the%20manufacturer%20in%20May%20after%20the%20company%20said%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-workers-falsely-reported-performing-checks-on-787-wings-fuselage-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emay%20not%20have%20properly%20inspected%20its%20787%20Dreamliner%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FAA%20is%20investigating%20whether%20Boeing%20completed%20the%20inspections%20and%20whether%20company%20employees%20may%20have%20falsified%20aircraft%20records%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20Boeing%20was%20re-inspecting%20all%20787%20jets%20in%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Alaska%20blowout%20incident%2C%20the%20FAA%20ordered%20Boeing%20to%20produce%20an%20action%20plan%20to%20address%20its%20safety%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20said%20this%20week%20that%20it%20was%20continuing%20%26quot%3Bto%20hold%20Boeing%20accountable%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20conducted%20a%20review%20of%20that%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFAA%20Administrator%20Michael%20Whitaker%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20does%20not%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20our%20increased%20oversight%20of%20Boeing%20and%20its%20suppliers%2C%20but%20it%20sets%20a%20new%20standard%20of%20how%20Boeing%20does%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing's%20issues%20have%20also%20seen%20it%20hit%20with%20criticism%20from%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20customers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-ceo-tells-boeing-get-your-act-together-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmirates%20CEO%20Sheikh%20Ahmed%20bin%20Saeed%20Al%20Maktoum%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20planemaker%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20your%20act%20together%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-boeing-everett-hound-mechanics-keep-quiet-over-safety-concerns-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717329027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661fa3cd20b15f0ff428a829%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-boeing-everett-hound-mechanics-keep-quiet-over-safety-concerns-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing's%20Everett%20site%20in%20Washington%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20manufacturing%20buildings%2C%20produces%20the%20747%2C%20767%2C%20777%2C%20and%20787%20airplanes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nrennolds%40insider.com%20(Nathan%20Rennolds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-boeing-everett-hound-mechanics-keep-quiet-over-safety-concerns-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gavaskar%20bats%20for%20Kohli%20to%20open%20alongside%20Rohit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717328983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110640918%2Cimgsize-57166.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fits-very-good-to-talk-on-tv-about-gavaskar-bats-for-kohli-to-open-alongside-rohit%2Farticleshow%2F110640747.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cricketing%20community%20is%20buzzing%20with%20discussions%20about%20whether%20Virat%20Kohli%20should%20open%20alongside%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20in%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20This%20debate%20has%20intensified%20following%20Kohli's%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20where%20he%20topped%20the%20charts%20as%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20with%20741%20runs%20in%2015%20innings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20BJP%20Keeps%20Winning%20In%20Northeast%3F%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20Explains%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20explained%20why%20the%20BJP%20keeps%20winning%20elections%20and%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20northeast%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%2C%20the%20Earth%20Sciences%20Minister%2C%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20simultaneously%20in%20the%20mountainous%20border%20state.%20The%20BJP%20has%20reclaimed%20power%20in%20the%20Arunachal%20assembly%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term%20today%2C%20securing%20a%20majority%20with%2046%20seats%20in%20the%2060-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20seats%20the%20BJP%20lost%20are%20with%20a%20thin%20margin%2C%20but%2046%20seats%20mean%20a%20huge%20victory%20for%20the%20Arunachal%20people.%20The%20region%20has%20seen%20real%20development.%20There%20has%20been%20real%20transformation%20across%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20told%20NDTV.%20He%20contested%20from%20Arunachal%20West.%20The%20other%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20Arunachal%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20factor%20is%20PM%20Modi%20ji's%20visionary%20leadership.%20The%20region%20is%20most%20difficult%20in%20terms%20of%20geography%20and%20topography%20-%20to%20have%20airport%2C%20railway%20lines%2C%20villages%20connected%20with%20roads%2C%20this%20was%20an%20impossible%20task%20in%20the%20past.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20won%20this%20election%20with%20a%20comfortable%20margin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20transformational%20change%20the%20people%20have%20seen%20gives%20no%20other%20party%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20elections%20in%20the%20northeast.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20chapter%20is%20closed.%20They%20did%20nothing%20for%2060%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20the%20northeast%20has%20always%20voted%20for%20the%20power%20in%20the%20Centre.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20never%20had%20a%20government%20in%20the%20Centre%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Congress%20had.%20So%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20say%20the%20northeast%20goes%20with%20the%20government%20in%20the%20Centre.%20In%202015%2C%20Arunachal%20became%20the%20first%20state%20to%20be%20governed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Modi%20ji%20became%20PM%20in%202014.%20Then%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Assam%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Tripura%2C%20and%20formed%20alliance%20governments%20in%20Meghalaya%20and%20Sikkim%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20northeast%20now%20feels%20somebody%20listens%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20marathon%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024%20-%20spread%20over%20six%20weeks%2C%20the%20second-longest%20general%20election%20since%201951-52%20-%20a%20big%20win%20for%20the%20ruling%20BJP-led%20NDA%20has%20been%20predicted%20by%20twelve%20exit%20polls%20-%20India%20Today-%20Axis%20My%20India%20(361-401)%2C%20News%2024-Today's%20Chanakya%20(400)%2C%20ABP%20News-C%20Voter%20(353-383)%2C%20Republic%20Bharat-%20P%20Marq%20(359)%2C%20India%20News-%20D-Dyanamics%20(371)%2C%20Republic%20Bharat-%20Matrize%20(353-368)%2C%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%20(281-350)%2C%20News%20Nation%20(342-378)%2C%20TV%209%20Bharatvarsh-%20Polstrat%20(342)%2C%20Times%20Now-ETG%20(358)%2C%20India%20TV-%20CNX%20(362-392)%20and%20Jan%20Ki%20Baat%20(362-392).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exit%20polls%20have%20also%20predicted%20NDA%20dominance%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra%20and%20Left-led%20alliance's%20rout%20in%20Kerala.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20the%20exit%20polls%20predicted%20a%20better%20performance%20for%20the%20BJP%20than%20it%20did%20the%20last%20time%20(22).%20Most%20exit%20polls%20have%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20now%20be%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20Bengal%20in%20terms%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717328880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fereh24k8_kiren-rijiju_625x300_02_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-why-bjp-keeps-winning-in-northeast-kiren-rijiju-explains-to-ndtv-5800651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20explained%20why%20the%20BJP%20keeps%20winning%20elections%20and%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20northeast%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-why-bjp-keeps-winning-in-northeast-kiren-rijiju-explains-to-ndtv-5800651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-why-bjp-keeps-winning-in-northeast-kiren-rijiju-explains-to-ndtv-5800651%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-