%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658d5b7d0b8e1c832ca6c9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20some%20rough%20years%2C%20Huawei%20carried%20on%20through%20the%202000s.%3Cp%3ESTR%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202008%20and%202009%2C%20contract%20sales%20increased%20by%2046%25%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20which%20came%20from%20overseas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20generated%20close%20to%20%2423.3%20billion%20in%20revenue%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSN01324096%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20was%20also%20seeking%20to%20expand%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFollowing%20the%20success%20of%20its%20smartphones%2C%20Huawei%20expanded%20into%20wearable%20devices%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Yu%2C%20CEO%20of%20Huawei's%20consumer%20business%20group%2C%20launches%20the%20new%20watch%20GT2%20at%20the%20Convention%20Center%20in%20Munich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658ceacd0b8e1c832ca62dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20the%20success%20of%20its%20cellphones%2C%20Huawei%20has%20ventured%20into%20more%20smart%20devices.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Dalder%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20company%20released%20the%20Huawei%20watch%2C%20which%20combined%20typical%20watch%20functions%20with%20modern%20smartwatch%20features.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%202019%2C%20the%20telecom%20giant%20seemed%20to%20be%20leading%20the%205G%20revolution%20for%20faster%20wireless%20connection%20globally%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226112%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ren%20Zhengfei%20huawei%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6bccc3262898527629