r%20change.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20we%20are%20here%20for%20the%20long%20haul%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20go.%20Hope%20you%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20response%20came%20after%20Kerala%20Congress%20questioned%20EaseMyTrip%20on%20X%2C%20highlighting%20the%20company's%20earlier%20decision%20to%20remove%20Maldives%20from%20their%20platform%20as%20a%20show%20of%20support%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20questioned%20the%20resumption%20of%20bookings%2C%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20online%20travel%20aggregator%20%40EaseMyTrip%20made%20a%20nationalistic%20move%20by%20removing%20the%20Maldives%20as%20a%20destination%20from%20their%20flight%20and%20hotel%20booking%20platform%20to%20support%20PM%20Modi.%20Now%20they%20have%20quietly%20resumed%20booking%20to%20Maldives.%20We%20are%20wondering%20what%20happened.%20Is%20it%20a%20sign%20of%20something%3F%20Is%20money%20more%20important%20than%20PM%20Modi%3F%20Money%20will%20come%20and%20go%2C%20and%20so%20is%20PM%20Modi!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20screenshots%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20Maldives%20bookings%20available%20on%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20prompting%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20company%20had%20reversed%20its%20boycott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishant%20Pitti%20clarified%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20boycott%20remains%20in%20place%20and%20any%20future%20changes%20would%20be%20formally%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEaseMyTrip%20initially%20halted%20operations%20in%20Maldives%20in%20January%20after%20three%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20following%20his%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20flight%20bookings%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20made%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20government%2C%20impacted%20240%2C000%20annual%20bookings%20through%20their%20platform.%20Prashant%20Pitti%2