%20and%20those%20of%20some%20corporates%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20conglomerate%20may%20be%20in%20focus%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20companies%20are%20perceived%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20BJP's%20pro-growth%20policies%20and%20their%20outpeformance%20may%20extend%20in%20case%20of%20a%20strong%20election%20result%2C%20a%20CLSA%20note%20said.%20Engineering%20giant%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Ltd.%2C%20and%20power%20generators%20NTPC%20Ltd.%20and%20NHPC%20Ltd.%20are%20among%20CLSA's%20preferred%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESentiment%20will%20also%20be%20buoyed%20by%20faster-than-expected%20economic%20growth%20data%2C%20published%20after%20market%20hours%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20gross%20domestic%20product%20grew%20more%20than%208%25%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%20that%20ended%20in%20March%2C%20cementing%20the%20nation's%20position%20as%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-how-markets-may-react-to-the-outcome-5783396%5C%22%3E3%20Possible%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Outcomes%20And%20How%20Markets%20Could%20React%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Ratings%20recently%20indicated%20a%20potential%20credit%20rating%20upgrade%20for%20India%2C%20boosting%20financial%20markets%20ahead%20of%20the%20country's%20inclusion%20in%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.'s%20emerging%20market%20bond%20index%20later%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20bond%20market%2C%20many%20things%20have%20been%20positive%20of%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Saurabh%20Bhatia%2C%20head%20of%20macro%20strategy%20and%20fixed%20income%20at%20Sapient%20Finserv%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20election%20outcome%20may%20give%20further%20fillip.%20%26quot%3BA%20strong%20government%20leads%20to%20more%20fiscal%20discipline%20and%20macro%20stability.%20Bonds%20will%20rejoice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategy%20views%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarley%20Capital%20(Andrei%20Stetsenko%2C%20partner%20and%20portfolio%20manager)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20we%20see%20a%20renewed%20push%20to%20implement%20long-stymied%20but%20potentially%20economically%20transformative%20reforms%20to%20politically-sensitive%20areas%20such%20as%20agriculture%2C%20labor%20laws%2C%20and%20land%20acquisition%2C%20there%20would%20be%20potential%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BIndia%20premium%26quot%3B%20to%20other%20emerging%20markets%20to%20widen%20even%20further%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%2C%20however%2C%20that%20political%20capital%20ends%20up%20focused%20more%20on%20potentially%20divisive%20social%20issues%2C%20I'd%20expect%20the%20opposite%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuantum%20Advisors%20(Nilesh%20Shetty%2C%20portfolio%20manager)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20consensus%20view%20was%20that%20PM%20Modi%20would%20come%20back%20and%20exit%20polls%20reaffirm%20that%20view.%20Any%20opportunistic%20shorts%20will%20cover%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20near-term%20rally%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%20election%20results%20have%20not%20mattered%20much%20as%20average%20GDP%20growth%20has%20hovered%20around%206.5%25%20irrespective%20of%20the%20government%20in%20power%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrust%20Mutual%20Fund%20(Sandeep%20Bagla%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEquity%2C%20currency%2C%20and%20bond%20markets%20should%20greet%20the%20exit%20poll%20results%20with%20a%20renewed%20enthusiasm%20as%20the%20uncertainty%20regarding%20poll%20verdict%20is%20finally%20getting%20over%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20likely%20buoyancy%20in%20the%20rupee%2C%20bonds%20should%20be%20well%20supported%20and%20there's%20a%20distinct%20possibility%20that%20the%201