y%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%2C%20Ira%20included%20every%20single%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20in%20the%20user%20group.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20women%20across%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20primarily%20contacts%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20provide%20detailed%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20the%20scepticism%20around%20people%20using%20menstrual%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20told%20me%20that%20India%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20such%20a%20product%20and%20that%20women%20should%20stick%20to%20traditional%20methods.%20I%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20because%20I%20am%20a%20user%20of%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20myself%2C%20and%20it%20has%20transformed%20my%20life.%20I%20can%20sleep%20through%20the%20night%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261342%2Farpita-double-amputee-yoga-fitness-instructor-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20swim%2C%20do%20yoga%2C%20and%20run%20half%20a%20%3C%2Fa%3Emarathon%20comfortably.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20experience%2C%20along%20with%20the%20positive%20feedback%20from%20my%20early%20user%20group%E2%80%94including%20domestic%20workers%20and%20other%20women%20who%20adapted%20to%20the%20cup%20instantly%E2%80%94showed%20me%20that%20not%20only%20are%20women%20ready%20for%20this%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20calling%20out%20for%20it%20because%20the%20current%20products%20are%20of%20poor%20quality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Ira%E2%80%99s%20personal%20experience%20and%20the%20experiences%20of%20women%20around%20her%20that%20gave%20her%20the%20conviction%20to%20challenge%20those%20who%20said%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20and%20insertable%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20need%20was%20there%2C%E2%80