ited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Sharda%20Godara.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716813891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharda%20Godara%20transformed%20her%20Faridabad%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20jungle%20with%201%2C000%20plants.%20She%20now%20enjoys%20crafting%20miniature%20tray%20gardens%20around%20various%20themes%2C%20and%20shares%20five%20steps%20to%20create%20them%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350852%2Fhow-to-make-miniature-tray-gardens-at-home-steps-faridabad-sharda-godara-urban-gardener%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20%E2%80%98Eco%20Village%20Lady%E2%80%99%20of%20India%20Who%20Uses%20Solar%20Energy%20to%20Power%20Villages%20in%20Ladakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20a%20revolution%2C%20one%20has%20to%20step%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20comfort%20zone.%20This%20became%20clear%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Neha%20Upadhyaya%20right%20at%20the%20outset%20of%20her%20quest%20to%20transform%20the%20rural%20hinterland%20of%20India%2C%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20Ladakhi%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%20a%20decade%20since%20that%20bold%20decision%2C%20and%20Upadhyaya%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20prouder%20of%20the%20ripple%20effect%20her%20efforts%20created%20%E2%80%94%20impacting%20more%20than%203%2C000%20women%20through%20her%20platform%20Guna%20Organics%20and%20also%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20eight%20rural%20nooks%20being%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335875%2Fgoa-stay-lawyer-panta-ferrao-built-khaama-kethna-eco-village-jungle-retreat-tree-house-cottage%2F%5C%22%20t